des:
Beautiful Piano: Relaxing Sound
Beautiful Piano music is a great background sound for studying , working, reading or writing. This helps to focus, alleviate stress and improve productive capacity. 

How to use "Beautiful Piano: Relaxing Sound"?

You can say:
- "Alexa, open Beautiful Piano"
- "Alexa, start Beautiful Piano"
- "Alexa, play Beautiful Piano"

It will automatically play the sound indefinitely until you say "Alexa, stop".
